    "en": {
      "title": "Pohottuwa's support for Acting President Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It has been decided to give the support of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna to Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe, who has been appointed as the Acting President, in the election of a Member of Parliament for the currently vacant position of President.",
        "This was decided in a discussion held by the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna group of MPs. Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma of the independent member group from the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna has also announced that he will contest for the presidency."
      ],
